VYDBUr YHVH 'aL-MShH L'aMUr.
DBUr 'aL-BNY YShUr'aL L'aMUr NPhSh KY-ThChT'a BShGGH MKL MTShVTh YHVH 'aShUr L'a Th'yShYNH V'yShH M'aChTh MHNH.
'aM HKHN HMShYCh YChT'a L'aShMTh H'yM VHQUrYB 'yL ChT'aThV 'aShUr ChT'a PhUr BN- BQUr ThMYM LYHVH LChT'aTh.
VHBY'a 'aTh-HPhUr 'aL-PhThCh 'aHL MV'yD LPhNY YHVH VSMK 'aTh-YDV 'yL-Ur'aSh HPhUr VShChT 'aTh-HPhUr LPhNY YHVH.
VLQCh HKHN HMShYCh MDM HPhUr VHBY'a 'aThV 'aL-'aHL MV'yD.
VTBL HKHN 'aTh-'aTShB'yV BDM VHZH MN-HDM ShB'y Ph'yMYM LPhNY YHVH 'aTh-PhNY PhUrKTh HQDSh.
VNThN HKHN MN-HDM 'yL-QUrNVTh MZBCh QTUrTh HSMYM LPhNY YHVH 'aShUr B'aHL MV'yD V'aTh KL-DM HPhUr YShPhK 'aL-YSVD MZBCh H'yLH 'aShUr-PhThCh 'aHL MV'yD.
V'aTh-KL-ChLB PhUr HChT'aTh YUrYM MMNV 'aTh-HChLB HMKSH 'yL-HQUrB V'aTh KL- HChLB 'aShUr 'yL-HQUrB.
V'aTh ShThY HKLYTh V'aTh-HChLB 'aShUr 'yLYHN 'aShUr 'yL-HKSLYM V'aTh-HYThUrTh 'yL- HKBD 'yL-HKLYVTh YSYUrNH.
K'aShUr YVUrM MShVUr ZBCh HShLMYM VHQTYUrM HKHN 'yL MZBCh H'yLH.
V'aTh-'yVUr HPhUr V'aTh-KL-BShUrV 'yL-Ur'aShV V'yL-KUr'yYV VQUrBV VPhUrShV.
VHVTShY'a 'aTh-KL-HPhUr 'aL-MChVTSh LMChNH 'aL-MQVM THVUr 'aL-ShPhK HDShN VShUrPh 'aThV 'yL-'yTShYM B'aSh 'yL-ShPhK HDShN YShUrPh.
V'aM KL-'yDTh YShUr'aL YShGV VN'yLM DBUr M'yYNY HQHL V'yShV 'aChTh MKL-MTShVTh YHVH 'aShUr L'a-Th'yShYNH V'aShMV.
VNVD'yH HChT'aTh 'aShUr ChT'aV 'yLYH VHQUrYBV HQHL PhUr BN-BQUr LChT'aTh VHBY'aV 'aThV LPhNY 'aHL MV'yD.
VSMKV ZQNY H'yDH 'aTh-YDYHM 'yL-Ur'aSh HPhUr LPhNY YHVH VShChT 'aTh-HPhUr LPhNY YHVH.
VHBY'a HKHN HMShYCh MDM HPhUr 'aL-'aHL MV'yD.
VTBL HKHN 'aTShB'yV MN-HDM VHZH ShB'y Ph'yMYM LPhNY YHVH 'aTh PhNY HPhUrKTh.
VMN-HDM YThN 'yL-QUrNTh HMZBCh 'aShUr LPhNY YHVH 'aShUr B'aHL MV'yD V'aTh KL- HDM YShPhK 'aL-YSVD MZBCh H'yLH 'aShUr-PhThCh 'aHL MV'yD.
V'aTh KL-ChLBV YUrYM MMNV VHQTYUr HMZBChH.
V'yShH LPhUr K'aShUr 'yShH LPhUr HChT'aTh KN Y'yShH-LV VKPhUr 'yLHM HKHN VNSLCh LHM.
VHVTShY'a 'aTh-HPhUr 'aL-MChVTSh LMChNH VShUrPh 'aThV K'aShUr ShUrPh 'aTh HPhUr HUr'aShVN ChT'aTh HQHL HV'a.
'aShUr NShY'a YChT'a V'yShH 'aChTh MKL-MTShVTh YHVH 'aLHYV 'aShUr L'a-Th'yShYNH BShGGH V'aShM.
'aV-HVD'y 'aLYV ChT'aThV 'aShUr ChT'a BH VHBY'a 'aTh-QUrBNV Sh'yYUr 'yZYM ZKUr ThMYM.
VSMK YDV 'yL-Ur'aSh HSh'yYUr VShChT 'aThV BMQVM 'aShUr-YShChT 'aTh-H'yLH LPhNY YHVH ChT'aTh HV'a.
VLQCh HKHN MDM HChT'aTh B'aTShB'yV VNThN 'yL-QUrNTh MZBCh H'yLH V'aTh-DMV YShPhK 'aL-YSVD MZBCh H'yLH.
V'aTh-KL-ChLBV YQTYUr HMZBChH KChLB ZBCh HShLMYM VKPhUr 'yLYV HKHN MChT'aThV VNSLCh LV.
V'aM-NPhSh 'aChTh ThChT'a BShGGH M'yM H'aUrTSh B'yShThH 'aChTh MMTShVTh YHVH 'aShUr L'a- Th'yShYNH V'aShM.
'aV HVD'y 'aLYV ChT'aThV 'aShUr ChT'a VHBY'a QUrBNV Sh'yYUrTh 'yZYM ThMYMH NQBH 'yL-ChT'aThV 'aShUr ChT'a.
VSMK 'aTh-YDV 'yL Ur'aSh HChT'aTh VShChT 'aTh-HChT'aTh BMQVM H'yLH.
VLQCh HKHN MDMH B'aTShB'yV VNThN 'yL-QUrNTh MZBCh H'yLH V'aTh-KL-DMH YShPhK 'aL-YSVD HMZBCh.
V'aTh-KL-ChLBH YSYUr K'aShUr HVSUr ChLB M'yL ZBCh HShLMYM VHQTYUr HKHN HMZBChH LUrYCh NYChCh LYHVH VKPhUr 'yLYV HKHN VNSLCh LV.
V'aM-KBSh YBY'a QUrBNV LChT'aTh NQBH ThMYMH YBY'aNH.
VSMK 'aTh-YDV 'yL Ur'aSh HChT'aTh VShChT 'aThH LChT'aTh BMQVM 'aShUr YShChT 'aTh- H'yLH.
VLQCh HKHN MDM HChT'aTh B'aTShB'yV VNThN 'yL-QUrNTh MZBCh H'yLH V'aTh-KL-DMH YShPhK 'aL-YSVD HMZBCh.
V'aTh-KL-ChLBH YSYUr K'aShUr YVSUr ChLB-HKShB MZBCh HShLMYM VHQTYUr HKHN 'aThM HMZBChH 'yL 'aShY YHVH VKPhUr 'yLYV HKHN 'yL-ChT'aThV 'aShUr-ChT'a VNSLCh LV.
